{"tid":784999,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打試過告醫生/醫院醫療疏忽？","createTime":"2018-08-18T19:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T23:43:29.000Z","uid":24679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"03c1c951962ae564378e517aa4e412c8c71c07a0","tid":784999,"uid":24679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T19:07:40.000Z","msg":"我屋企人發生左意外<br />\n之前係某間私家醫院做左兩次手術（駁神經線&amp;筋）<br />\n然後一路有keep 住做物理治療同埋有其他醫生跟進<br />\n但發現做完手術後康復未達理想預期<br />\n<br />\n有另一位醫生發現做手術果位醫生駁漏左一條筋，如果再做手術既話要多十幾萬<br />\n但小弟為左屋企人做手術已經借左廿幾萬已經還到hihi 咁<br />\n真係好難再借多十幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽聞哩d 情況係唔係可以告醫生/醫院方面有疏忽<br />\n請問有冇巴打遇過哩d 情況同埋最後賠償會係點？"},{"pid":"93f933298bc5644cf979817f76b07a5e2d9015e0","tid":784999,"uid":195904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T19:18:15.000Z","msg":"有個醫生做做下手術行撚左去<br />\n到而家仲撈到風生水起"},{"pid":"bd4a4f4496cdcf8c80ce19a6cdd2005c083b66a4","tid":784999,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T19:25:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59e65461a4ae23fff8e2125ed53481dfb78f56d6","tid":784999,"uid":24679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd4a4f4496cdcf8c80ce19a6cdd2005c083b66a4","tid":784999,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T19:25:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"個醫生唔肯，話最多都係醫生手術費收平d"},{"pid":"5fa4a4af1e5131a23ffd41dc1b34b275824c9065","tid":784999,"uid":71748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"排公立"},{"pid":"8ea61a0176589f347ca4704873db544a87b28dd9","tid":784999,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06185ea8d23fa44551acd5e2917a93a7a3c4d7f4","tid":784999,"uid":24679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ea61a0176589f347ca4704873db544a87b28dd9","tid":784999,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike